        <title>2D Fantasy sprite bundle</title>
        <published>2024-11-29T21:20:17+00:00</published>
        <updated>2024-11-30T13:24:14+00:00</updated>
        
        <author>
          <name>
            
              yzzfo
            
          </name>
        </author>
        
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://yzzfo.github.io/en/unitys/2d-fantasy-sprite-bundle/"/>
        <id>https://yzzfo.github.io/en/unitys/2d-fantasy-sprite-bundle/</id>
        
        <content type="html" xml:base="https://yzzfo.github.io/en/unitys/2d-fantasy-sprite-bundle/">&lt;p&gt;Create unique landscapes with sprite shapes and hand-drawn sprites,perfect for 2d games like side-scrollers or platformers.&lt;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;2D Fantasy sprite bundle is a bundle that includes 9 assets wtih a price discount of ~50%.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;Assets in bundle:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;215282&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Island sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;216237&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Forest sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;215783&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Dungeon sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;217340&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Mountains sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;215558&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Old forest sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;220769&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Ice and Snow sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;230552&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Lava dungeon sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;242096&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Desert sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;223980&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Underwater sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;u3d.as&#x2F;32mP&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Spring forest sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;slug&#x2F;259443&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Crystal dungeon sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;u3d.as&#x2F;3fCZ&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Abandoned station sprite pack&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;Roadmap for this Bandle:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;-Asian theme ,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-Flying lands sprite pack ,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;-Mechanical area sprite pack .&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;and more....&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
